hopobject.body: Where do you study? walmart bahia pharmacy Lindsay Lohan has posed for almost as many mug shot photos as she has magazine shoots. The troubled starlet left a California courtroom in cuffs on Oct. 19 after a fed-up judge yanked her probation for blowing off court-ordered community service. She's already gone to jail three times previously, only to exit early because of overcrowding issues. A spokesman for the troubled starlet said Lohan was looking forward to her next hearing.
